flowchart TD
    REQ[Unified Agent Request] --> INT[Intent Router]
    INT --> SUP[Support Agent]
    INT --> SAL[Sales Agent]
    INT --> ANA[Analytics Agent]

    SUP --> MCP[MCP Tool Layer]
    SAL --> MCP
    ANA --> MCP

    MCP --> TOOL1[Demand Forecast Tool]
    MCP --> TOOL2[Anomaly Detection Tool]
    MCP --> TOOL3[Customer Segment Tool]
    MCP --> TOOL4[Dashboard Metrics Tool]
    MCP --> TOOL5[Product Search Tool]
    MCP --> TOOL6[Rebuild Knowledge Tool]

    SUP --> RET[Retrieval Layer]
    RET --> VEC[Local Vector Store]
    RET --> EMB[Azure Embeddings]

    SUP --> CHAT[Azure Chat]
    SAL --> CHAT
    ANA --> CHAT
